projects.name: TechTrolley-Enhancing The Retail Experience
projects.description: The smart shopping trolley system aims to enhance the traditional shopping experience by incorporating modern technologies. Developed an Android application using Java, a Flask API and PostgresSQL for backend functionality, and a Python Tkinter interface for the user interface. Project utilizes ESP32 microcontrollers and RFID technology for interaction with the physical shopping trolley.
